Noc u kuci moje majke;;1991;;NC;;Drama;;6.8;;Zarko Dragojevic;;Igor Pervic,Zumreta Ibrahimovic,Ljubisa Samardzic,Danica Maksimovic,Stojan 'Stole' Arandjelovic,Petar Bozovic,Olja Beckovic,Faruk Begolli,Ivan Bekjarev,Slavko Stimac,Nenad Nedinic,Petar Ilic,Dusica Zegarac,Dusan Janicijevic,Miodrag 'Miki' Krstovic,Vladan Zivkovic,Momcilo Muric,Veljko Marinkovic;;A love story of a couple coming from different social backgrounds set in the context of Yugoslavian reality, its social and state decline. Their quest for the meaning of life proves to be nothing but failure.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0180876/